content: Dear friends, hello to all of you!
some information to all of you.
Renjuclass students will soon have a new kind of renju happiness - the online tournament.
This is the first time event, organised by our senior members.
I am very happy for this idea,
and I hope you all will enjoy the tournament.
Perhaps GGM yyfcsd will introduce this idea here closely, please.

Signups for the 1st ORC online tournament has opened. Welcome all renjuclass students to join.
For detailed information, please read here: http://ns02.compute.com.tw/~renjuclass/departments/theory/nnrs/tournament/tournaments.html
hope more class members can join the big party
